2009.11.21

	* 0.3.3 version:

	* respawn.c: Apply "setlinebuf()" to "stdout" and "stderr" to
	reduce buffering delays.

2010.02.14

	* 0.3.4 version:

	* respawn.c: Print human-readable timestamp.
	* ASSERT.h, ASSERT.c, DEBUG.h: debugging functions.
	* COMPILER.h: compiler's options.
	* LOG.h, LOG.c: run time logging functions.
	* x_time.h, x_time.c: time manipulation functions.

2012.12.31

	* 0.4 version:

	* respawn.c: Pass SIGHUP, SIGINT, SIGQUIT, SIGUSR1, SIGUSR2, SIGTERM
	signals to child. Terminate itself if child terminated on SIGTERM
	signal.
